      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/11/83",
      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنِ اَلرَّجُلِ يَشْتَرِي سِهَامَ اَلْقَصَّابِينَ مِنْ قَبْلِ أَنْ يَخْرُجَ اَلسَّهْمُ قَالَ \"إِنِ اِشْتَرَى سَهْماً فَهُوَ بِالْخِيَارِ إِذَا خَرَجَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3854 - Al-Hasan bin Mahbub narrated from Zayd Al-Shahham who said:\nI asked Abu Abdillah (as) about a man who purchases shares from butchers before the shares are distributed.\nImam (as) said: \"If he purchases a share, then he has the option to accept or reject it when it is distributed.\""
        ]
      }
    },
